    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294950/extras/c829519891349377da29a11d31109ee5.avif?t=1749467484\" width=300 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>                                            </strong>        </i><strong>它是一只狗，它讨厌正方形。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294950/extras/f968e0a2e841aa356ed77309c5056d4d.avif?t=1749467484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294950/extras_big/f968e0a2e841aa356ed77309c5056d4d.avif?t=1749467484 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                      你就是它头脑中的声音，必须帮助摧毁所有的方块。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294950/extras/94aa13f240b5b6a4bd304844cf25bb0c.poster.avif?t=1749467484\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294950/extras/94aa13f240b5b6a4bd304844cf25bb0c.webm?t=1749467484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294950/extras/94aa13f240b5b6a4bd304844cf25bb0c.mp4?t=1749467484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                                                  </strong>   <strong>这是安东。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>akabos</strong></i> 是一款点击游戏，你需要点击你的狗狗来摧毁方块。 游戏有完整的剧情和多个结局，取决于你的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\